          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-1" n="1">Wou'd you rise in the Church, be stupid and dull,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-2" n="2">Be empty of Learning, of insolence full;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-3" n="3">Tho^ lewd and immorral, be formal and grave,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-4" n="4">In flatt'ring, an Artist; in fawning, a Slave.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-5" n="5">No Merit, no Science, no Virtue i\s·<hi rend="italics">apparently·overwriting·</hi>n\ wanting.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-6" n="6">In him, that's accomplish'd in cringing and Canting.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-7" n="7">Be Studious to practise true meaness of Spirit:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-8" n="8">And who, but L<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. Bolton was Mitred for Merit?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-9" n="9">Wou'd you wish to be wrap'd in a Rochet?── in short</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-807-002H-line-10" n="10">Be as pox'd and prophane as fanatical H────</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
